## Limitations

The analysis is based on available literature up to October 2023, and the rapidly evolving nature of the pandemic means that new developments could alter the current understanding. Additionally, the impact of COVID-19 varies across regions and industries, which may not be fully captured in this report. The findings are also contingent on the sources reviewed, which may not encompass all perspectives on the topic.